# Helm templates in this directory are GENERATED at build time by the
# nix/game/deployment.nix derivation (`helmTemplates pkgs`). The flake's
# `helmChart` output copies CRDs from this chart source dir but writes
# templates/*.yaml, values.yaml, and Chart.yaml fresh on every build.
#
# Do not commit template files here; they would diverge from the
# generated artifacts. See ../../nix/game/deployment.nix.
